19Ps 3:5 I lie down and sleep; I wake again, because the LORD sustains me.
19Ps 3:6 I will not fear the tens of thousands drawn up against me on every side.
19Ps 3:7 Arise, O LORD! Deliver me, O my God! Strike all my enemies on the jaw; break the teeth of the wicked.
