19Ps 44:23 Awake, O Lord! Why do you sleep? Rouse yourself! Do not reject us forever.
19Ps 44:24 Why do you hide your face and forget our misery and oppression?
19Ps 44:25 We are brought down to the dust; our bodies cling to the ground.
19Ps 44:26 Rise up and help us; redeem us because of your unfailing love.
