19Ps 119:154 Defend my cause and redeem me; preserve my life according to your promise.
19Ps 119:155 Salvation is far from the wicked, for they do not seek out your decrees.
19Ps 119:156 Your compassion is great, O LORD; preserve my life according to your laws.
