19Ps 119:166 I wait for your salvation, O LORD, and I follow your commands.
19Ps 119:167 I obey your statutes, for I love them greatly.
19Ps 119:168 I obey your precepts and your statutes, for all my ways are known to you.
19Ps 119:169 May my cry come before you, O LORD; give me understanding according to your word.
19Ps 119:170 May my supplication come before you; deliver me according to your promise.
19Ps 119:171 May my lips overflow with praise, for you teach me your decrees.
19Ps 119:172 May my tongue sing of your word, for all your commands are righteous.
19Ps 119:173 May your hand be ready to help me, for I have chosen your precepts.
19Ps 119:174 I long for your salvation, O LORD, and your law is my delight.
19Ps 119:175 Let me live that I may praise you, and may your laws sustain me.
19Ps 119:176 I have strayed like a lost sheep. Seek your servant, for I have not forgotten your commands.
